## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-103">此类实现<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-103">This class implements the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> class.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="07015-104">从.NET Framework 2.0 开始，我们建议您创建<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>使用的实例<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法和<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings>类，以充分利用新功能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-104">Starting with the .NET Framework 2.0, we recommend that you create <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instances by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings> class to take advantage of new functionality.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-105">`XmlTextWriter` 维护与当前元素堆栈中定义的所有命名空间对应的命名空间堆栈。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-105">`XmlTextWriter` maintains a namespace stack corresponding to all the namespaces defined in the current element stack.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-106">使用`XmlTextWriter`可以手动声明命名空间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-106">Using `XmlTextWriter` you can declare namespaces manually.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
w.WriteStartElement("root");  
w.WriteAttributeString("xmlns", "x", null, "urn:1");  
 w.WriteStartElement("item","urn:1");  
 w.WriteEndElement();  
 w.WriteStartElement("item","urn:1");  
 w.WriteEndElement();  
w.WriteEndElement();  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-107">上面的 C# 代码生成以下输出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-107">The above C# code produces the following output.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-108">`XmlTextWriter` 将升级到根元素，以避免使其重复上两个子元素的命名空间声明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-108">`XmlTextWriter` promotes the namespace declaration to the root element to avoid having it duplicated on the two child elements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-109">子元素中选取从命名空间声明的前缀。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-109">The child elements pick up the prefix from the namespace declaration.</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<root xmlns:x="urn:1">  
 <x:item/>  
 <x:item/>  
</x:root>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-110">`XmlTextWriter` 此外允许你重写当前命名空间声明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-110">`XmlTextWriter` also allows you to override the current namespace declaration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-111">在以下示例中，命名空间 URI"123""abc"要生成的 XML 元素通过重写`<x:node xmlns:x="abc"/>`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-111">In the following example, the namespace URI "123" is overridden by "abc" to produce the XML element `<x:node xmlns:x="abc"/>`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
w.WriteStartElement("x","node","123");  
w.WriteAttributeString("xmlns","x",null,"abc");  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-112">通过使用采用作为自变量的前缀的写入方法还可以指定要使用的前缀。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-112">By using the write methods that take a prefix as an argument you can also specify which prefix to use.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-113">在以下示例中，两个不同的前缀映射到相同的命名空间 URI 生成的 XML 文本`<x:root xmlns:x="urn:1"><y:item xmlns:y="urn:1"/></x:root>`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-113">In the following example, two different prefixes are mapped to the same namespace URI to produce the XML text `<x:root xmlns:x="urn:1"><y:item xmlns:y="urn:1"/></x:root>`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XmlTextWriter w = new XmlTextWriter(Console.Out);  
w.WriteStartElement("x","root","urn:1");  
 w.WriteStartElement("y","item","urn:1");  
 w.WriteEndElement();  
w.WriteEndElement();  
w.Close();  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-114">如果有多个不同的前缀映射到同一个命名空间 URI 的命名空间声明`XmlTextWriter`向后遍历的命名空间声明堆栈并选取最近的一个。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-114">If there are multiple namespace declarations mapping different prefixes to the same namespace URI, `XmlTextWriter` walks the stack of namespace declarations backwards and picks the closest one.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XmlTextWriter w = new XmlTextWriter(Console.Out);  
w.Formatting = Formatting.Indented;  
w.WriteStartElement("x","root","urn:1");  
w.WriteStartElement("y","item","urn:1");  
w.WriteAttributeString("attr","urn:1","123");  
w.WriteEndElement();  
w.WriteEndElement();  
w.Close();  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-115">在上面的 C# 示例，因为`WriteAttributeString`调用未指定前缀，编写器使用推入命名空间堆栈的最后一个前缀，并将生成以下 XML:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-115">In the above C# example, because the `WriteAttributeString` call does not specify a prefix, the writer uses the last prefix pushed onto the namespace stack, and produces the following XML:</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<x:root xmlns:x="urn:1">  
 <y:item y:attr="123" xmlns:y="urn:1" />  
</x:root>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-116">如果出现命名空间冲突，`XmlTextWriter`通过生成替换前缀来解决它们。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-116">If namespace conflicts occur, `XmlTextWriter` resolves them by generating alternate prefixes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-117">例如，如果某属性和元素具有相同前缀但不同的命名空间，`XmlWriter`生成替换前缀的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-117">For example, if an attribute and element have the same prefix but different namespaces, `XmlWriter` generates an alternate prefix for the attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-118">生成的前缀命名`n{i}`其中`i`是从 1 开始的数字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-118">The generated prefixes are named `n{i}` where `i` is a number beginning at 1.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-119">编号为 1。 对于每个元素重置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-119">The number is reset to 1 for each element.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-120">与命名空间 URI 相关联的属性必须具有前缀 （默认值特性不适用于命名空间）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-120">Attributes which are associated with a namespace URI must have a prefix (default namespaces do not apply to attributes).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-121">这符合 XML 建议中的 W3C 命名空间的 5.2 部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-121">This conforms to section 5.2 of the W3C Namespaces in XML recommendation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-122">如果属性引用命名空间 URI，但不是指定前缀，则编写器将生成属性的前缀。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-122">If an attribute references a namespace URI, but does not specify a prefix, the writer generates a prefix for the attribute.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-123">在编写时的空元素，一个额外的空格之间添加标记名称和结束标记，例如`<item />`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-123">When writing an empty element, an additional space is added between tag name and the closing tag, for example `<item />`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-124">这提供了与旧版浏览器兼容性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-124">This provides compatibility with older browsers.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-125">当`String`用作方法参数`null`和`String.Empty`是等效的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-125">When a `String` is used as method parameter, `null` and `String.Empty` are equivalent.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-126">`String.Empty` 遵循 W3C 规则。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-126">`String.Empty` follows the W3C rules.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-127">若要编写强类型化的数据，使用<xref:System.Xml.XmlConvert>类，以将数据类型转换为字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-127">To write strongly typed data, use the <xref:System.Xml.XmlConvert> class to convert data types to string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-128">例如，下面的 C# 代码将转换中的数据`Double`到`String`编写元素和`<price>19.95</price>`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-128">For example, the following C# code converts the data from `Double` to `String` and writes the element `<price>19.95</price>`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
Double price = 19.95;  
writer.WriteElementString("price", XmlConvert.ToString(price));  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-129">`XmlTextWriter` 不会检查以下：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-129">`XmlTextWriter` does not check for the following:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="07015-130">属性和元素名称中的无效字符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-130">Invalid characters in attribute and element names.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="07015-131">不符合指定的编码的 Unicode 字符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-131">Unicode characters that do not fit the specified encoding.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-132">如果 Unicode 字符不符合指定的编码，`XmlTextWriter`未转义的字符实体到 Unicode 字符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-132">If the Unicode characters do not fit the specified encoding, the `XmlTextWriter` does not escape the Unicode characters into character entities.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="07015-133">重复的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-133">Duplicate attributes.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="07015-134">中的 DOCTYPE 公共标识符或系统标识符的字符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-134">Characters in the DOCTYPE public identifier or system identifier.</span></span>  
  
## <a name="security-considerations"></a><span data-ttu-id="07015-135">安全注意事项</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-135">Security Considerations</span></span>  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-136">以下各项是使用时应考虑的事项<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-136">The following items are things to consider when working with the <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> class.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="07015-137">引发的异常<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter>可能会泄露冒泡到应用程序不希望的路径信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-137">Exceptions thrown by the <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> can disclose path information that you do not want bubbled up to the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-138">应用程序必须捕获异常并进行相应的处理。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-138">Your applications must catch exceptions and process them appropriately.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="07015-139">在将 <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> 传递给另一个应用程序时，基础流会公开给该应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-139">When you pass the <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> to another application the underlying stream is exposed to that application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-140">如果需要将 <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> 传递给不完全可信的应用程序，应使用通过 <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> 方法创建的 <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A> 对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-140">If you need to pass the <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> to a semi-trusted application, you should use an <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> object created by the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A> method instead.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="07015-141"><xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter>不会验证传递到任何数据<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.WriteDocType%2A>或<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.WriteRaw%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-141">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> does not validate any data that is passed to the <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.WriteDocType%2A> or <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.WriteRaw%2A> methods.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-142">不应将任意数据传递给这些方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-142">You should not pass arbitrary data to these methods.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="07015-143">如果更改默认设置，则无法保证生成的输出是格式正确的 XML 数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-143">If the default settings are changed, there is no guarantee that the generated output is well-formed XML data.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="07015-144">如不接受支持组件，<xref:System.Text.Encoding>来自受信任的源对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-144">Do not accept supporting components, such as an <xref:System.Text.Encoding> object, from an untrusted source.</span></span>

  
  
## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="07015-188">从.NET Framework 2.0 开始，我们建议您创建<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>使用的实例<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法和<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings>类，以充分利用新功能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-188">Starting with the .NET Framework 2.0, we recommend that you create <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instances by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings> class to take advantage of new functionality.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-189">如果`Indented`设置选项，则子元素将使用缩进<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.Indentation%2A>和<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.IndentChar%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-189">If the `Indented` option is set, child elements are indented using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.Indentation%2A> and <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.IndentChar%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-190">缩进仅元素内容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-190">Only element content is indented.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-191">下面的 C# 代码写出 HTML 元素，包括混合的内容：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-191">The following C# code writes out HTML elements including mixed content:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XmlTextWriter w = new XmlTextWriter(Console.Out);   
 w.Formatting = Formatting.Indented;   
 w.WriteStartElement("ol");   
 w.WriteStartElement("li");   
 w.WriteString("The big "); // This means "li" now has a mixed content model.  
 w.WriteElementString("b", "E");   
 w.WriteElementString("i", "lephant");   
 w.WriteString(" walks slowly.");   
 w.WriteEndElement();   
 w.WriteEndElement();  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-192">上面的代码生成以下输出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-192">The above code produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<ol>   
  <li>The big <b>E</b><i>lephant</i> walks slowly.</li>   
</ol>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07015-193">这在 HTML 中查看时不出现空白粗体和斜体元素之间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-193">When this is viewed in HTML no white space appears between the bold and italic elements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-194">事实上，在此示例中，如果这些元素之间添加缩进"大象"一词可能会错误地遭到破坏。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-194">In fact, in this example, if indenting was added between these elements the word "Elephant" would be incorrectly broken.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="07015-195">编写内容，不包括任何文本`String.Empty`将该元素放入混合内容模式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-195">Writing any text content, excluding `String.Empty` puts that element into mixed content mode.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-196">子元素不会继承此"混合"模式状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-196">Child elements do not inherit this "mixed" mode status.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-197">"混合"元素的子元素进行缩进，除非它是也包含"混合"的内容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-197">A child element of a "mixed" element does indenting, unless it is also contains "mixed" content.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07015-198">元素内容 (http://www.w3.org/TR/1998/REC-xml-19980210#sec-element-content)和混合内容 (http://www.w3.org/TR/1998/REC-xml-19980210#sec-mixed-content)根据 XML 1.0 定义这些术语的定义。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07015-198">Element content (http://www.w3.org/TR/1998/REC-xml-19980210#sec-element-content) and mixed content (http://www.w3.org/TR/1998/REC-xml-19980210#sec-mixed-content) are defined according to the XML 1.0 definitions of these terms.</span></span>  
  
   
  
